abstract: >
  Reproducibility kit for the paper "A KDD-Governed Agentic Architecture for
  Race Engineering: From Telemetry to Evidence-Grounded Decision Support".
  Contains the LaTeX manuscript, synthetic datasets, experimental results,
  analysis notebooks, generation scripts, and reviewer package.
